    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在《Strike Mission》中展开激烈的空中军事战役吧！这是一款俯视角动作游戏，你将扮演精英飞行员杰克·沃克，在关键任务中拯救世界免遭全球科技威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏具有沉浸式玩法、战术雷达系统、每关多个目标以及电影式过场动画，Strike Mission 将快节奏动作、策略与剧情完美结合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁成就，证明你就是世界需要的英雄。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>入侵敌方领土</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/6fb71d826285bc67f7151b463f3abb5b.poster.avif?t=1752842476\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/6fb71d826285bc67f7151b463f3abb5b.webm?t=1752842476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/6fb71d826285bc67f7151b463f3abb5b.mp4?t=1752842476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>摧毁敌方建筑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/987b0085760bec420bec4563414b924b.poster.avif?t=1752842476\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/987b0085760bec420bec4563414b924b.webm?t=1752842476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/987b0085760bec420bec4563414b924b.mp4?t=1752842476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>对抗军舰作战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118880/extras/2cbd78bea65be22480e0c820dd083b90.poster.avif?t=1752842476\" width=300 hei